This is my first CSS map, I based it on the east side of CoD's Harbor map. This is a Fight Yard version, I have made some updates due to some of the feed back I received from the previous version.

   -=UPDATES=-
There are now 16 spawn points
changed some textures
retooled some buildings
fixed the drywall area
added lighting effects
retooled some of the enviornment
other map adjustments 


Hope you have as much fun killing on it as I had building it.

Maggs
